---
title: The best home-service companies in North Texas — and what they cost
description: Independent rankings of the best HVAC and home-service companies across Dallas–Fort Worth, plus researched cost ranges for major home projects. Published methodology, no lead-gen funnels.
layout: base.njk
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1>The best home-service pros in North Texas — and what the work actually costs</h1>
  <p>We rank Dallas–Fort Worth's HVAC and home-service companies on a published methodology, and research real installed-cost ranges so you can walk into any bid knowing what's normal. No lead-gen forms, no inflated "free quote" funnels.</p>
  <p class="hero-links"><a href="/best-hvac/">Best HVAC by city</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="/tools/ac-cost-calculator/">Estimate your AC cost</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="/methodology/">How we rank</a></p>
</section>

{% if collections.reviews.length %}
<section class="cat-group">
  <h2>Best HVAC companies by city</h2>
  <p class="lede">Each city ranking weighs installation track record, pricing transparency, warranty and verified ratings — sources cited, updated monthly.</p>
  <div class="cards">
    {% for r in collections.reviews %}
    <a class="card" href="{{ r.url }}">
      <h3>{{ r.data.cityName }} HVAC companies</h3>
      <p>{{ r.data.cardBlurb }}</p>
      <span class="meta-row"><span class="tag">{{ r.data.placement }}</span><span class="updated">Updated {{ r.data.updated | readableDate }}</span></span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if collections.guides.length %}
  {% set cats = [] %}
  {% for g in collections.guides %}
    {% if g.data.category and cats.indexOf(g.data.category) == -1 %}
      {% set _ = cats.push(g.data.category) %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

  <h2 class="section-divider">Home project cost guides</h2>
  {% for cat in cats %}
  <section class="cat-group">
    <h3 class="cat-head">{{ cat }}</h3>
    <div class="cards">
      {% for g in collections.guides %}
        {% if g.data.category == cat %}
        <a class="card" href="{{ g.url }}">
          <h3>{{ g.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ g.data.description }}</p>
          <span class="updated">Updated {{ g.data.updated | readableDate }}</span>
        </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endfor %}

  {% set uncategorized = [] %}
  {% for g in collections.guides %}
    {% if not g.data.category %}{% set _ = uncategorized.push(g) %}{% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  {% if uncategorized.length %}
  <section class="cat-group">
    <h3 class="cat-head">More guides</h3>
    <div class="cards">
      {% for g in uncategorized %}
      <a class="card" href="{{ g.url }}">
        <h3>{{ g.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ g.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="updated">Updated {{ g.data.updated | readableDate }}</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
{% endif %}
